author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
🎟️ To see Justin Hawkins Rides Again LIVE across the UK, visit: 
https://www.aegpresents.co.uk/event/justin-hawkins-rides-again/

Esteemed YouTuber and Master of the BEHS, Danny Sapko, has started his own band called Mellon-Collies.  So Danny and Mellon-Collies singer, Keira Mellon, joined me to talk music, hidden superpowers and catching out Fil from Wings of Pegasus....
🎟️ To see the Mellon-Collies at the 1 in 12 Club in Bradford, you can find tickets here: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/christmas-with-the-mellon-collies-tickets-1833318959359

To see more from Flash Cassette: https://www.youtube.com/@UCXuSj2SPpWJjyUKH8-sig8A and the Mellon-Collies https://www.youtube.com/@Mellon-Collies and of course Danny: https://www.youtube.com/@UCPVjQ58A0BujzVMEmFCJ3hA  Wings of Pegasus is here: https://www.youtube.com/@UCEHCXnggyvkw1uaTChZ_kuA 

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

🎟️ To see The Dark
